{"tha-ap60:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap60:0.2":"Bijanivagga ","tha-ap60:0.3":"Dhajadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap60:1.1":"“Padumuttarabuddhassa, ","tha-ap60:1.2":"bodhiya padaputtame; ","tha-ap60:1.3":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap60:1.4":"dhajamaropayim aham. ","tha-ap60:2.1":"Patitapattani ganhitva, ","tha-ap60:2.2":"bahiddha chaddayim aham; ","tha-ap60:2.3":"Antosuddham bahisuddham, ","tha-ap60:2.4":"adhimuttamanasavam. ","tha-ap60:3.1":"Sammukha viya sambuddham, ","tha-ap60:3.2":"avandim bodhimuttamam; ","tha-ap60:3.3":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap60:3.4":"ahutinam patiggaho. ","tha-ap60:4.1":"Bhikkhusanghe thito sattha, ","tha-ap60:4.2":"ima gatha abhasatha; ","tha-ap60:4.3":"‘Imina dhajadanena, ","tha-ap60:4.4":"upatthanena cubhayam. ","tha-ap60:5.1":"Kappanam satasahassam, ","tha-ap60:5.2":"duggatim so na gacchati; ","tha-ap60:5.3":"Devesu devasobhagyam, ","tha-ap60:5.4":"anubhossatinappakam. ","tha-ap60:6.1":"Anekasatakkhattunca, ","tha-ap60:6.2":"raja ratthe bhavissati; ","tha-ap60:6.3":"Uggato nama namena, ","tha-ap60:6.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap60:7.1":"Sampattim anubhotvana, ","tha-ap60:7.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap60:7.3":"Gotamassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap60:7.4":"sasanebhiramissati’. ","tha-ap60:8.1":"Padhanapahitattomhi, ","tha-ap60:8.2":"upasanto nirupadhi; ","tha-ap60:8.3":"Dharemi antimam deham, ","tha-ap60:8.4":"sammasambuddhasasane. ","tha-ap60:9.1":"Ekapannasasahasse, ","tha-ap60:9.2":"kappe uggatasavhayo; ","tha-ap60:9.3":"Pannasasatasahasse, ","tha-ap60:9.4":"khattiyo meghasavhayo. ","tha-ap60:10.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap60:10.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap60:10.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap60:11.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma dhajadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap60:12.1":"Dhajadayakattherassapadanam atthamam. "}